---
title: Sweet and Sticky Chicken Thigh Noodles with Mushrooms and Green Beans
description: This Sweet and Sticky Chicken Thigh Noodles is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
